<sect1 id="dir_3c2debfdd2bfc5d375ae885ec56c77d2_1autotoc_md469">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::messaging</title><para>Communication infrastructure for commands and events within the game loop.</para>
<para>This module provides the messaging backbone for the helios engine. It includes the Command pattern implementation for buffering and executing game actions, as well as event buses for decoupled inter-system communication.</para>
</sect1>
